{
  "stem": "3631.6",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm very nervous about what's going on in the country-- the-- the mood of confrontation, confrontation, the mood of-- of hatred.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Instead of-- instead of cooperating, they-- they-- they confront each other and try-- everybody wants to have his-- his way is the only way.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the world cannot live like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I'm-- I'm concerned about this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And one of the reasons I have, maybe, some of these things when-- that I brought to the attention of general public and general-- in different countries, maybe it will rub a little bit off.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Maybe they say, gee, you don't have to follow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The school kids said, if we can tell the school, the students, maybe, you don't have to-- there's a leader who-- who leads you on to some things.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Maybe you don't have to do it, if you don't feel like.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Maybe you can just think about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And this is what we really have to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The-- the Holocaust is no longer a-- a Jewish-- it is part of Jewish history, but it-- it's not only Jewish history.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It is part of the history of World War II.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It's part of world history-- all countries were involved, through action, or through non-action.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It is something that concerns the world, and not only Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And that has to be brought to the attention of people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I hope that, whatever Spielberg is doing with this, and I hope whatever I'm doing, or the different museums, that that has a little influence on the world.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "If it does, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But you have to try.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'll be happy to.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'd like you to meet Martha, my wife, Martha Dressler.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have been married since 1957.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Is that right?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's correct.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I would.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
